and feature relationships\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Effective Customer Grouping: Cluster customers for targeted marketing and personalization\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Improved Data Quality Assessment: Detect and address issues like missing values\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Informed Decision-Making: Use visual and statistical insights for strategic decisions\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Optimized Resource Allocation: Allocate efforts efficiently across customer segments\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n",
